<h2>Actions</h2>

<p>Finally, this component fires an action on tap/click. Actions are passed as [closure actions](https://dockyard.com/blog/2015/10/29/ember-best-practice-stop-bubbling-and-use-closure-actions). The action will not be fired if the component is disabled.</p>

